These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: lavender, amber
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, social-worker
2 different games are played: whist, monopoly
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski
1. the person who likes lavender is on the far right##1
2. the person playing whist is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the designer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Color       | amber       | lavender |
| Job         | social-worker | designer  |
| Game       | monopoly    | whist    |
| Transport   | jet-ski       | bike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
2 different games are played: poker, monopoly
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, bike
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, time-travel
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, surfing
1. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Game      | monopoly     | poker |
| Transport           | airplane | bike      |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel  | action      |
| Sport         | snowboarding | surfing     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk
There 2 different types of food: apple, avocado
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: tennis, swimming
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, time-travel
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is the person watching time-travel movies##1
3. the person eating apple is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | soy-milk  |
| Food          | apple    | avocado   |
| Sport   | swimming  | tennis   |
| Movie-Genre     | time-travel     | musical |

