2 different games are played: chess, scrabble
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: lacrosse, weightlifting
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, techno
1. the fan of punk is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea       | soy-milk |
| Game          | scrabble         | chess    |
| Sport           | weightlifting | lacrosse    |
| Music-Genre   | punk           | techno   |

