The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, marigold
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the analyst##1
3. the person watching adventure movies is the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Job           | analyst  | mechanic   |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure  | musical      |
| Sport         | climbing | volleyball |
| Flower     | marigold     | amaryllis |

