.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, security-guard
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, cain
2 different pets are kept: mouse, rabbit
City: edinburgh, boston
1. the coach is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
2. the coach is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
3. the owner of the mouse is the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Job           | security-guard | coach     |
| Cigar   | oliveros          | cain |
| Pet           | mouse          | rabbit    |
| City     | boston            | edinburgh       |

 